    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《地牢横冲直撞》中踏上充满动作元素的冒险之旅，这款经典的在线多人地牢探索游戏，迎来终极复兴！与好友组队或独自作战，一路杀入充满怪物的地牢。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053950/extras/9403d438f6399853cda8f811da5d6ecb.poster.avif?t=1771340699\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053950/extras/9403d438f6399853cda8f811da5d6ecb.webm?t=1771340699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053950/extras/9403d438f6399853cda8f811da5d6ecb.mp4?t=1771340699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从众多独具特色的英雄中选择你的冠军。每位英雄都拥有独特的技能、武器和游戏风格。无论你喜欢狂战士的蛮力、吸血鬼猎人的狡猾陷阱，还是火焰术士的元素风暴，总有一款英雄适合你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053950/extras/f88829b2b6973f12f283e26a284e77f8.avif?t=1771340699\" width=720 height=229 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提升英雄等级，增强他们的能力，并自定义你的装备配置！数百种不同的武器可供装备，你可以根据自己的策略微调你的装备组合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053950/extras/bb7ab0b2fcfa94f494986806c613eaf5.poster.avif?t=1771340699\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053950/extras/bb7ab0b2fcfa94f494986806c613eaf5.webm?t=1771340699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053950/extras/bb7ab0b2fcfa94f494986806c613eaf5.mp4?t=1771340699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与最多 3 位好友组队，或与社区玩家对战，闯过充满致命陷阱、隐藏宝藏的地牢！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053950/extras/85b920951c815f0321239bdb182e8976.poster.avif?t=1771340699\" width=800 height=632 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053950/extras/85b920951c815f0321239bdb182e8976.webm?t=1771340699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053950/extras/85b920951c815f0321239bdb182e8976.mp4?t=1771340699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >招募宠物加入你的战场，看着它们代替你消灭敌人：犀牛、狼、龙等等，任你选择！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053950/extras/33453bcfe5d2af1396232461940e2824.avif?t=1771340699\" width=800 height=269 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >程序生成的地下城带来了无限的重玩价值。每次游玩都会面临全新的挑战，从规模庞大的 Boss 战到巧妙隐藏的秘密，应有尽有。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053950/extras/0e0081e31d9f63720e66c2a4aada5405.avif?t=1771340699\" width=800 height=468 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏体验原汁原味，并进行了诸多优化！《地牢横冲直撞》最初于 2012 年在 脸书 上发布，并于 2017 年关闭。随着 Flash 的正式停止支持，这款游戏也随之消失，800 万玩家失去了家园。如今，我们已恢复了这款游戏，并在努力完善和扩展游戏内容的同时，对原有的游戏体验进行了现代化改造。地牢里见，韭菜们！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053950/extras/f4689e667fbec95c2732ede24c9de385.poster.avif?t=1771340699\" width=800 height=632 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053950/extras/f4689e667fbec95c2732ede24c9de385.webm?t=1771340699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053950/extras/f4689e667fbec95c2732ede24c9de385.mp4?t=1771340699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
